headline: CME Group Global Head of Commodities to Present at 2026 Raymond James Annual Institutional Investors Conference
summary: CME Group, the world's leading derivatives marketplace, today announced that Derek Sammann, Senior Managing Director, Global Head of Commodities, will present at the 47th annual Raymond James Institutional Investors Conference on Tuesday, March 3, 2026, at 9:15 a.m. (Eastern Time).
